lead_paragraph: Barcelona coach Luis Enrique has urged his players to keep their heads in Sunday’s crucial local derby at home to Espanyol, where his side could clinch a 24th La Liga title.

headline.print_headline: Barca Must Keep Their Heads and Focus on Football-Luis Enrique
